<help general group>

Group either displays your present group, or adds one to your group if
you are the leader and they are following you and in your room.

syntax:  group		Displays your group.
	 group all	Add everyone following you to your group.
	 group garath   Attempts to add Garath to your group.
<color=red>
See also:  ungroup, follow, gs, assist
</color></help>
